Interface IndexFieldData<FD extends AtomicFieldData>

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGeoPointDVIndexFieldData, AbstractGeoPointDVIndexFieldData.GeoPointDVIndexFieldData, AbstractIndexFieldData, AbstractIndexOrdinalsFieldData, BinaryDVIndexFieldData, BytesBinaryDVIndexFieldData, DisabledIndexFieldData, GeoPointArrayIndexFieldData, GlobalOrdinalsIndexFieldData, IndexIndexFieldData, PagedBytesIndexFieldData, ParentChildIndexFieldData, ParentChildIndexFieldData.GlobalFieldData, SortedNumericDVIndexFieldData, SortedSetDVOrdinalsIndexFieldData

    public interface IndexFieldData<FD extends AtomicFieldData>
extends IndexComponent
    Thread-safe utility class that allows to get per-segment values via the load(LeafReaderContext) method.
